N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 134.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

This Part applies to entry onto and work upon the right of
way of State highways under the jurisdiction of the Commissioner of

Transportation to control, maintain, or otherwise affect vegetation located
upon such right of way for the purpose of enhancing the visibility of
advertising signs. Notes
